---
import Breadcrumbs from '../../../components/Breadcrumbs.astro'
import Layout from '../../../layouts/Layout.astro'
---
<Layout title="Jimmy Connoley - Co-Founder, Rank4AI | AI Search Strategist" description="Jimmy Connoley is co-founder of Rank4AI. AI search strategist specialising in entity clarity and citation architecture for UK businesses.">

<article class="pt-12 pb-24 reveal">
  <div class="container-narrow">
    <Breadcrumbs items={[
      { label: 'Home', href: '/' },
      { label: 'About', href: '/about/' },
      { label: 'Team', href: '/about/team/' },
      { label: 'Jimmy Connoley' }
    ]} />

    <div class="flex items-center gap-5 mb-8 mt-6">
      <div class="w-20 h-20 rounded-full bg-teal text-text-light flex items-center justify-center text-2xl font-bold flex-shrink-0">JC</div>
      <div>
        <h1 class="!text-3xl mb-1">Jimmy Connoley</h1>
        <p class="text-accent font-medium">Co-Founder, Rank4AI</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <h2 class="mt-10 mb-4">Background</h2>
    <p class="text-[17px] text-text-muted leading-relaxed mb-5">Jimmy is the co-founder of Rank4AI, a UK AI search agency focused on improving visibility and recommendation likelihood across ChatGPT, Claude, Gemini, Perplexity, Copilot and Google AI.</p>
    <p class="text-[17px] text-text-muted leading-relaxed mb-5">12 years in B2B growth strategy, business development and commercial performance. Previously scaled digital products and built partnerships with Harvard, Mayo Clinic, Columbia and Kaiser Permanente. Now focused entirely on AI search visibility.</p>

    <h2 class="mt-10 mb-4">Expertise</h2>
    <p class="text-[17px] text-text-muted leading-relaxed mb-5">Jimmy focuses on the structural side of AI visibility. How businesses are described across directories, listings and professional platforms. How those descriptions align or conflict. And how AI systems use that information to decide who to recommend.</p>

    <h2 class="mt-10 mb-4">Approach</h2>
    <p class="text-[17px] text-text-muted leading-relaxed mb-5">Boutique agency. No SaaS products. No juniors. No handoffs. Just hands-on work with every client. We do not do work you cannot understand. If something does not make sense, we explain it.</p>

    <div class="mt-10 pt-8 border-t border-border">
      <h2 class="!text-xl mb-4">Related</h2>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-3">
        <a href="/about/team/adam-parker/" class="card group text-sm"><span class="font-medium text-teal group-hover:text-accent">Adam Parker</span></a>
        <a href="/about/five-signal-framework/" class="card group text-sm"><span class="font-medium text-teal group-hover:text-accent">Five Signal Model</span></a>
        <a href="/what-we-do/ecosystem-services/" class="card group text-sm"><span class="font-medium text-teal group-hover:text-accent">Ecosystem Services</span></a>
        <a href="/free-audit/" class="card group text-sm"><span class="font-medium text-accent">Get a Free Audit &rarr;</span></a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</article>

<!-- Person Schema -->
<script type="application/ld+json" set:html={JSON.stringify({
  "@context": "https://schema.org",
  "@type": "Person",
  "name": "Jimmy Connoley",
  "jobTitle": "Co-Founder",
  "worksFor": { "@type": "Organization", "name": "Rank4AI", "url": "https://www.rank4ai.co.uk" },
  "description": "Co-Founder of Rank4AI. 12 years in B2B growth strategy, business development and commercial performance. Focused on AI search visibility and entity clarity.",
  "knowsAbout": ["Entity clarity", "Citation architecture", "AI ecosystem validation", "B2B AI search"],
  "url": "https://www.rank4ai.co.uk/about/team/jimmy-connoley/"
})} />

</Layout>
